<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Recover 2FA Setup - STINGFU</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0f0f 0%, #1a1a1a 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 420px;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .recover-box {
            background: rgba(30, 35, 45, 0.95);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 40px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            color: #8a8a8a;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .info-box {
            background: rgba(74, 158, 255, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(74, 158, 255, 0.3);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        
        .info-box h3 {
            color: #4a9eff;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .info-box p {
            color: #b0b0b0;
            font-size: 13px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        input[type="email"],
        input[type="password"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            background: rgba(45, 50, 60, 0.8);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            border-radius: 10px;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 15px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        input::placeholder {
            color: #6a6a6a;
        }
        
        input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #4a9eff;
            background: rgba(45, 50, 60, 1);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(74, 158, 255, 0.1);
        }
        
        .error-message {
            background: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.15);
            border: 1px solid rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.3);
            color: #ff6b6b;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .btn-recover {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a9eff 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .btn-recover:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(74, 158, 255, 0.3);
        }
        
        .links {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 25px;
            padding-top: 25px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        
        .links a {
            color: #4a9eff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .links a:hover {
            color: #6ab0ff;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        .steps {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        
        .steps li {
            color: #a0a0a0;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="recover-box">
            <h1>Recover 2FA Setup</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Access your Google Authenticator QR code</p>
            
            <div class="info-box">
                <h3>Why do I need this?</h3>
                <p>If you created an account but didn't complete the 2FA setup, or if you need to set up Google Authenticator on a new device, enter your credentials below to access your QR code.</p>
            </div>
            
            <% if (error) { %>
                <div class="error-message"><%= error %></div>
            <% } %>
            
            <form method="POST" action="/recover-2fa">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="email">Email Address</label>
                    <input type="email" 
                           id="email" 
                           name="email" 
                           placeholder="your@email.com" 
                           required 
                           autofocus>
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="password">Password</label>
                    <input type="password" 
                           id="password" 
                           name="password" 
                           placeholder="Your account password" 
                           required>
                </div>
                
                <button type="submit" class="btn-recover">Access My QR Code</button>
            </form>
            
            <div class="info-box" style="margin-top: 25px; background: rgba(45, 50, 60, 0.5);">
                <h3>What happens next?</h3>
                <ol class="steps">
                    <li>We'll verify your credentials</li>
                    <li>You'll see your unique QR code</li>
                    <li>Scan it with Google Authenticator app</li>
                    <li>Enter the 6-digit code to verify</li>
                    <li>You're all set to login!</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
            
            <div class="links">
                <a href="/login">Back to Login</a> â€¢ 
                <a href="/signup">Create New Account</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>